data.name: broomtxt1.Text
data.value:
Right next to it was a picture of a man standing in the middle of a room that seemed familiar. It is you. Someone or something is behind you. A tall, lanky and dark silhouette is stood right behind you.
The book slipped right off your hands as you stumble forwards in a horrified trance. It was quickly broken by the haunting sound of footsteps that are quickly approaching you.
